title: Batang Baler - Batang Baler shared a link.
htmlTitle: Batang Baler - Batang Baler shared a link.
snippet:
Portion of the road from Baler to Manila is blocked due to landslide. Travellers 
from Baler, please do not to proceed to Manila in the meantime. Keep safe!
